ComicInfo.Title: What On Earth?
ComicInfo.Summary: Mombi banishes the attacking Freedom Fighters to Earth where they encounter death in the form of traffic, overhead power lines, gun-happy policemen, street gangs, helicopters and tanks! Their only hope of salvation comes in the form of the Earth dog, Max. And a volcano mysteriously appears and erupts in the middle of a once-quiet meadow to the south! Based on the Wonderful Wizard of Oz books.
